latestPosts.caption:
So thoughtful , imagine being in a cafe filled with notes written by people from all over the world 🩷

Sucha a beautiful cafe , the coffee tastes so much better, wasn’t expecting that a hyped up place on instagram would be worth it 🩷✨♥️😍!!! 

Please do visit @thenotecoffee ✨

Nestled by the serene Hoan Kiem Lake, this multistory café is a mosaic of heartfelt messages from around the globe. Every wall, chair, and corner is adorned with colorful sticky notes, each telling its own tale. From the famed egg coffee to refreshing coconut lattes, every sip here is a blend of flavor and sentiment. Don’t forget to pen your own note and become a part of this living tapestry!

.

.
